。[0,360]</li>\n<li>回复截止到今天晚上 10 点。</li>\n<li>最接近所有回复数字的平均值的 2/3 的数字为获胜数字。</li>\n<li>如有并列获胜的则取回复靠前的。</li>\n<li>请尊重社区规则，不要 spam 。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>奖品：50 元京东卡一张（或者 V 你 50 ）。</p>\n<p>由于大家的回复是公开的，所以和原版的博弈不太一样。规则似乎是有利于后回复的人，能看到先回复的信息。但如果获胜数字迅速缩小，先回复的就先占位置了。所以应该还算公平。。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1662698093, "replies": 616, "id": 878872}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 189849, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3554, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 357209, "username": "Mars2333", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Mars2333", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f562dbf51156e9fe9dd3fc0c47f88be7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f562dbf51156e9fe9dd3fc0c47f88be7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f562dbf51156e9fe9dd3fc0c47f88be7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1539936423, "last_modified": 1643267671}, "last_reply_by": "xiao109", "last_touched": 1662713892, "title": "你都是通过哪些渠道获取相对中立且正确的新闻？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/878787", "created": 1662684576, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1662684576, "replies": 168, "id": 878787}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 19581, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2289, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 593517, "username": "vite", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/vite", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "Seattle, WA", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e12/d729/593517_mini.png?m=1662633109", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e12/d729/593517_normal.png?m=1662633109", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e12/d729/593517_large.png?m=1662633109", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e12/d729/593517_xlarge.png?m=1662633109", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e12/d729/593517_xlarge.png?m=1662633109", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e12/d729/593517_xlarge.png?m=1662633109", "created": 1662384480, "last_modified": 1662633109}, "last_reply_by": "SuperXRay", "last_touched": 1662711460, "title": "Dynamic Island 灵动岛💊 软件放大硬件缺陷的典范之作", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/878717", "created": 1662635882, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天网上冲浪给我冲 emo 了，万万没想到 iPhone 14 Pro 这个药丸打孔竟然获得广大网友压倒性好评，不少人直呼惊艳，恨不得立马换机... 软件与硬件的完美结合？旁友们，请理智一点好么！\r\n\r\n我自 iPhone 4s 一路用过来，到 iPhone X 被刘海屏膈应住后停手，当时天真，心想库克能接受不完美的苹果，咱果粉不能，倒逼他回归正道指日可待，从此信念坚定的蹲一个全面屏。然而，苦等了五年，等到的却是配备丝滑动效的灵动岛，我只想说：王德发，库克你牛逼！\r\n\r\n一个硬件缺陷你不去解决硬件瓶颈，支配软件团队给你雕花，屎上雕花它是屎还是花？白瞎了苹果如此优秀的 UX 团队。我今天话撂这：库克不倒，苹果不会好。\r\n\r\n那么我等冥顽不灵的果黑还有希望么，唉，梦想还是要有的，万一实现了呢。诸位看看 Touch Bar 和 MagSafe 的前车之鉴，咱再等个四五年吧，把药丸扫入历史的垃圾堆。", "content_rendered": "<p>今天网上冲浪给我冲 emo 了，万万没想到 iPhone 14 Pro 这个药丸打孔竟然获得广大网友压倒性好评，不少人直呼惊艳，恨不得立马换机... 软件与硬件的完美结合？旁友们，请理智一点好么！</p>\n<p>我自 iPhone 4s 一路用过来，到 iPhone X 被刘海屏膈应住后停手，当时天真，心想库克能接受不完美的苹果，咱果粉不能，倒逼他回归正道指日可待，从此信念坚定的蹲一个全面屏。然而，苦等了五年，等到的却是配备丝滑动效的灵动岛，我只想说：王德发，库克你牛逼！</p>\n<p>一个硬件缺陷你不去解决硬件瓶颈，支配软件团队给你雕花，屎上雕花它是屎还是花？白瞎了苹果如此优秀的 UX 团队。我今天话撂这：库克不倒，苹果不会好。</p>\n<p>那么我等冥顽不灵的果黑还有希望么，唉，梦想还是要有的，万一实现了呢。诸位看看 Touch Bar 和 MagSafe 的前车之鉴，咱再等个四五年吧，把药丸扫入历史的垃圾堆。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1662636015, "replies": 102, "id": 878717}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 3455, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 913, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 508358, "username": "smd", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/smd", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/45cd/604c/508358_mini.png?m=1652683766", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/45cd/604c/508358_normal.png?m=1652683766", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/45cd/604c/508358_large.png?m=1652683766", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/45cd/604c/508358_xlarge.png?m=1652683766", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/45cd/604c/508358_xlarge.png?m=1652683766", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/45cd/604c/508358_xlarge.png?m=1652683766", "created": 1600241281, "last_modified": 1652683766}, "last_reply_by": "feller", "last_touched": 1662713657, "title": "最近每天都能收到招嫖短信……", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/878831", "created": 1662690649, "deleted": 0, "content": "### ios ，有没有好的解决方案", "content_rendered": "<h3>ios ，有没有好的解决方案</h3>\n", "last_modified": 1662690649, "replies": 102, "id": 878831}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/nav